comments: Iguodala (GSW) makes contact to the arm of Fox (SAC) during the drive and affects Fox's SQBR.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a picking position in the path of Fox (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Bagley III (SAC) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Durant (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a picking position in the path of Fox (SAC) and some contact occurs to his arms, but the contact is marginal.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Curry (GSW) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes marginal contact to the body of Curry (GSW) during his shooting motion before Fox (SAC) cleanly blocks his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes contact to the arm of Bagley III (SAC) before making contact with the ball during his shooting motion, and the contact affects Bagley III's driving shot attempt.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Green (GSW) sets the pick in the path of Fox (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LAR shows Green (GSW) briefly makes contact with Bagley III (SAC) during rebounding, but does not prevent him from getting to the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Durant (GSW) cleanly dislodges the ball from Hield (SAC) and the ball goes out of bounds off of Hield's leg.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Green (GSW).
Durant (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Hield (SAC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Barnes (SAC) briefly grasps Curry (GSW) around the waist but does not prevent him from disengaging from the pick.
Barnes (SAC) and Curry (GSW) make incidental contact with each other attempting to get to the loose ball.
Bagley III (SAC) commits a take foul on Iguodala (GSW).
Green (GSW) briefly grasps Bagley III (SAC) but does not prevent him from getting to the rebound.
Bogdanovic (SAC) briefly grasps Green (GSW) during the inbound, but allows him to disengage.
Thompson (GSW) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Hield (SAC).
